{"title":"'Hexo部署'","date":"2020-03-06T06:55:20.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年3月6日","L":"2020/03/06","MM-DD":"03-06"},"link":"2020/03/06/Hexodeploy","tags":["Hexo"],"updated":"2020-03-06T07:36:58.047Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>参考1：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/setup\" target=\"_blank\">HEXO官方文档</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>参考2：<a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000017986794\" target=\"_blank\">超详细Hexo+github搭建技术博客</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"安装准备\">安装准备<a href=\"#安装准备\" title=\"安装准备\"></a></h2><p>需要安装node.js和git两部分,找到对应系统的版本安装即可</p>\n<ul><li><p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/\" target=\"_blank\">nodejs</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://git-scm.com/download\" target=\"_blank\">git</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul><h2 id=\"安装hexo\">安装Hexo<a href=\"#安装hexo\" title=\"安装Hexo\"></a></h2><p>使用npm(一种包管理器，和python的pip，conda，centos使用的yum等类似)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果你的网络质量不好，可以使用镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g --registry&#x3D;镜像源</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>可用镜像源有：</p>\n<div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th align=\"center\">名称</th><th align=\"center\">URL</th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">淘宝NPM镜像</td><td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://registry.npm.taobao.org\" target=\"_blank\">https://registry.npm.taobao.org</a></td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">华为云镜像</td><td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://mirrors.huaweicloud.com/repository/npm/\" target=\"_blank\">https://mirrors.huaweicloud.com/repository/npm/</a></td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><p>然后执行以下命令来初始化</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init myBlog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>注意：这一条要会使用git来克隆相关文件到你本地的，记得挂上魔法上网工具，否则很慢很慢很慢。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>然后切换到myBlog目录下，使用<code>npm install</code>命令来自动地根据package.json文件来安装需要的依赖（有些依赖文件可能很大，执行的时候再安装比较轻量）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cd myBlog</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>网上所说的安装好目录是这样的</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── _config.yml # 网站的配置信息，您可以在此配置大部分的参数。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── package.json</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── scaffolds # 模版文件夹</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── source  # 资源文件夹，除 _posts 文件，其他以下划线_开头的文件或者文件夹不会被编译打包到public文件夹</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">| ├── _drafts # 草稿文件</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">| └── _posts # 文章Markdowm文件</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">└── themes # 主题文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>而我自己安装好是这样的，不清楚有什么区别</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── _config.yml # 网站的配置信息，您可以在此配置大部分的参数。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── package.json # 依赖项配置文件</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── package-lock.json</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── scaffolds # 模版文件夹</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── node_modules # hexo的依赖项</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── .gitignore</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">├── source  # 资源文件夹，除 _posts 文件，其他以下划线_开头的文件或者文件夹不会被编译打包到public文件夹</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">| └── _posts # 文章Markdowm文件</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">└── themes # 主题文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>然后输入以下命令来启动本地服务器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如果你和我一样用windows，会弹出相应的防火墙，点击允许即可。</p>\n<p>然后我们在浏览器输入<code>http://localhost:4000</code> 就可以看到你的博客了（本地）</p>\n<p>然后我们和github绑定在一起</p>\n","next":{"title":"Hello World","link":"2020/03/06/hello-world"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/03/06/Hexodeploy/","toc":[{"id":"安装准备","title":"安装准备","index":"1"},{"id":"安装hexo","title":"安装Hexo","index":"2"}]}